WEST NILE VIRUS, OFFER OF COLLABORATION (02)
**************************************
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
West Nile virus, overview & offer of collaboration 990927013327
West Nile-like virus - USA (New York City) 990925224146
